{# =========================================================
   🜂 TGK — Series / page Header Partial (v2.3)
   Purpose:
   Renders a concise title + description banner for pages
   (episodes, parts, or standalone teachings).

   ✅ Data Sources:
   • title          → main page title (from front matter)
   • description    → subheading / short summary
   • episode        → episode number (optional)
   • partNumeral    → Roman numeral (I, II, III)
   • partTitle      → optional part subtitle (future use)

   🧭 Behaviour:
   • Displays title, description, and meta line dynamically
   • Works for both episode-level and part-level pages
   • Safely hides missing fields without breaking layout

   ✨ Accessibility / SEO:
   • Uses <h1> for top-level page heading
   • Semantic meta block grouped under <div.page-meta>

   ⚙️ Styling:
   • Themed by pillar accent variables (e.g. --accent-color)
   • Usually followed by page content or tab navigation
   ========================================================= #}

<header class="series-header">
  <!-- 🪶 page Title -->
  <h1 class="page-title">
    {{ title or "Untitled page" }}
  </h1>

  <!-- 🗒️ Optional Description -->
  {% if description %}
    <p class="page-description">
      {{ description }}
    </p>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- 📜 Episode / Part Metadata -->
  <div class="page-meta">
    {% if episode %}
      <span class="page-episode">Episode {{ episode }}</span>
    {% endif %}
    {% if episode and partNumeral %} · {% endif %}
    {% if partNumeral %}
      <span class="page-part">Part {{ partNumeral }}</span>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</header>
